== To all Network Report Recipients in #{@organization.country_name}:

%p== This message is to inform you that #{@organization.name}'s application, based in #{@organization.country_name}, has been declined.

%p Due to administrative constraints, companies with less than ten direct employees (micro enterprises) will not be entered into the database of participating companies. However, we encourage micro enterprises to engage with their Global Compact Local Network.

%p For your records, the organization's profile and contact information are below.

%p Sincerely,
%p The Global Compact Office

%p
  %strong== Profile for #{@organization.name}:

- @row_style = 'text-align: right; padding-right: 10px'

%table
  %tr
    %td{:style => @row_style} Type:
    %td= @organization.organization_type_name
  %tr
    %td{:style => @row_style} Sector:
    %td= @organization.sector_name
  %tr
    %td{:style => @row_style} Employees:
    %td= @organization.employees
  %tr
    %td{:style => @row_style} Website:
    %td= @organization.url

%p
  %strong CEO / Highest Level Executive Information
%p
  %table
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Name:
      %td= @ceo.try(:full_name_with_title)
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Title:
      %td= @ceo.try(:job_title)
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Address:
      %td
        ==#{@ceo.address} #{@ceo.address_more}
        %br/
        ==#{@ceo.city} #{@ceo.state} #{@ceo.postal_code}
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Phone:
      %td= @ceo.phone
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Email:
      %td= @ceo.email

%p
  %strong Contact Point Information
%p
  %table
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Name:
      %td= @contact.full_name_with_title
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Title:
      %td= @contact.job_title
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Address:
      %td
        ==#{@contact.address} #{@contact.address_more}
        %br/
        ==#{@contact.city} #{@contact.state} #{@contact.postal_code}
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Phone:
      %td= @contact.phone
    %tr
      %td{:style => @row_style} Email:
      %td= @contact.email
